          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " on Twitter Tuesday that he is “constrained by law on some areas of rail regulation,” citing a law passed by Congress in 2015 that helped pave the way for the repeal of the brake requirement.",
