            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "That’s what the environmental groups are asking Buttigieg to do now. After years of sounding the alarm about the dangers of so-called “bomb trains” transporting liquefied natural gas and crude oil by rail — like the ",
